    Function reference

    API Access

    These functions provide access to a variety of data API.

    gdt_crr_get_data()
    Get abortion data from CRR Get the data for every country from the Center for Reproductive Rights.
    gdt_gutt_get_abortion_rates()
    Get abortion rate from the Guttmacher API
    gdt_hmd_birth_raw()
    HMD raw births data
    gdt_hmd_death_raw()
    HMD raw death data
    gdt_hmd_e0_table()
    Get life expectancy table from Human Mortality Database
    gdt_hmd_lex()
    Get life expectancy from the Human Mortality Database
    gdt_hmd_mortality()
    Get mortality table from Human Mortality Database
    gdt_hmd_population_raw()
    HMD raw population data
    gdt_idb_pyramid()
    One year population pyramid data (tidy)
    gdt_idb_pyramid_1y()
    One year population pyramid data (legacy function)
    gdt_idb_pyramid_5y()
    Return 5y population data
    gdt_ofs_vote_list()
    Get the swiss vote list
    gdt_table_demography()
    General demographic informations
    gdt_wb_demo()
    Demography data
    gdt_wb_lex()
    Life expectancy data

    gdt_opendata_swiss_geodata()

    gdt_opendata_swiss_geodata_json()
    Get swiss geodata in geojson format
